data.title: The Official NC STATE WOLFPACK Thread: Post your NC State Football & Alum Game Worn Stuff!!! [Archive]
data.meta_description:
Hi Guys, 
 
This thread is for North Carolina State Wolfpack football game worn memorabilia. Please post any game worn items on current or former Wolfpack football players. Also, please feel free to share any cool related stories or experiences. 
 
It's been a while since I posted any items. I'll kick this thread off with a few recently acquired pieces. Both of these are complementary to the Mei Gray Group. Barry was an absolute pleasure to do business with!! 
 
1) David Amerson Game Worn
